    "name": {
      "zh": "Custom Arms ST-EF 74 AK 金属框架枪托抵肩垫",
      "en": "AK Custom Arms ST-EF 74 skeleton stock extension"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "ST-EF",
      "en": "ST-EF"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "为 AK 平台武器系统金属框架枪托而设计的抵肩垫，其主要优势在于将 AKS 系列的金属折叠枪托的抵肩宽度增大至 AK-100 系列聚合物枪托同一水平，在迎合射手使用习惯的同时有效降低开火时的后座反冲。由 Custom Arms 设计制造。",
      "en": "A buttpad that extends the length of the standard metal frame folding buttstock of the AK-platform weapons. The advantage of this extension is that the width of the pad is equal to the width of the AK-100 series plastic pad. The buttpad adds comfort when shooting and reduces the recoil effect. Manufactured by Custom Arms."
    },
